snippet.title: Mr. Palmer
snippet.description:
I am Mr. Palmer and I am out for all the Baby Mama Terrorists and this unjust system! All I see is these Baby Mama Terrorists misusing their privileges and this unjust system supporting them! I want to show support for all fathers going through awful stuff due to the Baby Mama Terrorism! I provide support and strategies for men dealing with baby mama drama, child support, custody, and paternity issues! I will expose all these Baby Mama Terrorists.
